# pyenv
#   For a library or binary, you wish temporarily to have your preferred Python version
#   in the repository. For systems that require specific versions of Python, this can be
#   used to provide the necessary version.
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in cases where the project is not a package it can be excluded.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, it is generally recommended to include poetry.lock in version control.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
